---
title: Rosemary Roast Chicken & Red Wine Sauce with Broccoli Gratin & Cherry Tomato Salad
description: Time to celebrate the end of another year with a festive feast! For those of us who prefer a hot and hearty meal, this one’s a
winner - juicy, herby chicken with a luxurious red wine sauce and a creamy and crispy broccoli gratin on the side. Add a pop of freshness with a bright cherry tomato salad!
